{"title":"ML_Linear_Algebra","date":"2019-10-24T02:14:14.502Z","link":"2019/10/24/线性代数回顾","tags":["Machine Learning"],"updated":"2019-10-23T12:51:15.000Z","content":"<h4 id=\"矩阵和向量\">矩阵和向量<a href=\"2019/10/24/线性代数回顾#矩阵和向量\"></a></h4><p> <img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image37.PNG?raw=true\" alt=\"image\"><br> 矩阵的维数即行数x列数<br> Aij指第i行第j列。<br> 向量是一种特殊的矩阵，列向量<img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image37.2.PNG?raw=true\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"加法和标量乘法\">加法和标量乘法<a href=\"2019/10/24/线性代数回顾#加法和标量乘法\"></a></h4><ol>\n<li>矩阵的加法：行列数相等的可以加。<br><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image38.PNG?raw=true\" alt=\"image\"></li>\n<li>矩阵的乘法：每个元素都要乘。<br><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image38.2.PNG?raw=true\" alt=\"image\"><h4 id=\"矩阵向量乘法\"><a href=\"2019/10/24/线性代数回顾#矩阵向量乘法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"矩阵向量乘法\"></a>矩阵向量乘法</h4>矩阵和向量的乘法如图：<br><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image39.PNG?raw=true\" alt=\"image\"><h4 id=\"矩阵乘法\"><a href=\"2019/10/24/线性代数回顾#矩阵乘法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"矩阵乘法\"></a>矩阵乘法</h4></li>\n<li>m x n 矩阵乘于n x o 矩阵，变成m x o 矩阵。<br>如下两个矩阵A，B ：<br><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image40.PNG?raw=true\" alt=\"image\"><h4 id=\"乘法的性质\"><a href=\"2019/10/24/线性代数回顾#乘法的性质\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"乘法的性质\"></a>乘法的性质</h4></li>\n<li>矩阵的乘法不满足交换律</li>\n<li>矩阵的乘法满足结合律</li>\n<li>单位矩阵：从左上角到右下角的主对角线上的元素都为1其他全是0, 表示为I或E</li>\n<li>AA-1 = A-1A=I</li>\n<li>AI = IA = A<h4 id=\"矩阵的逆，转置\"><a href=\"2019/10/24/线性代数回顾#矩阵的逆，转置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"矩阵的逆，转置\"></a>矩阵的逆，转置</h4></li>\n<li>矩阵的逆：如果矩阵A（m * m）有逆矩阵则：AA-1=A-1A=I</li>\n<li>转置：<br><img src=\"https://github.com/jccjd/Coursera-Machine-Learning/blob/master/week-1/tu/image42.PNG?raw=true\" alt=\"image\"></li>\n<li>矩阵的转置基本性质:<br>(𝐴 ± 𝐵)𝑇 = 𝐴𝑇 ± 𝐵𝑇<br>(𝐴 × 𝐵)𝑇 = 𝐵𝑇 × 𝐴𝑇<br>(𝐴𝑇)𝑇 = 𝐴<br>(KA)T = KAT</li>\n</ol>\n","prev":{"title":"Hello World","link":"2019/10/24/hello-world"},"next":{"title":"README","link":"2019/10/24/README"},"plink":"http://jccjd.top/2019/10/24/线性代数回顾/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Jccjd","link":"<a href=\"http://jccjd.top/2019/10/24/线性代数回顾/\" title=\"ML_Linear_Algebra\">http://jccjd.top/2019/10/24/线性代数回顾/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"October 24, 2019","updated":"October 23, 2019"}}